## Lessons Learned

File [`LESSONS.md`](LESSONS.md) contains lessons from previous tasks.

**BEFORE a task:** Read `LESSONS.md` and check if any lesson applies to the current task.

**AFTER a task:** If you learned something new (bug, workaround, discovery), add a concise entry to the appropriate category in `LESSONS.md`. One entry = one line starting with `- **Title.** Content.`.
Must be absolute truth backed by facts, without a shadow of doubt, cannot be a guess.

